entropy.configuration.resources

Class ResourceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • entropy.configuration.resources.ResourceHandler

  • public class ResourceHandler
extends Object
    The link between a ResourceSpecification and a ReconfigurationProblem, that is, store the data related to the specifications in the problem
    Construct it with its ResourceSpecification, then associate(ReconfigurationProblem) it to the problem. This is then indexed by its specifications ' type in the problem's ReconfigurationProblem.#getUse(String), ReconfigurationProblem.#getUses() and ReconfigurationProblem.#getHandlers()
